      <title>美联储博斯蒂克：鉴于美国经济强劲，不急于降息</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/feds-bostic-no-urgency-cut-interest-rates-given-us-economys-strength-2024-03-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚特兰大联储主席拉斐尔·博斯蒂克在讲话中表示，鉴于经济和就业市场“繁荣”，美联储并未面临降息的紧迫压力，这强调了通胀可能陷入央行 2% 目标之上或什至被送往银行的风险。因“被压抑的繁荣”而更高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/feds-bostic-no-urgency-cut-interest-rates-given-us-economys-strength-2024-03-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 17:10:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
