      <title>由于内部控制问题损害了投资者的信任，NYCB 股价恢复下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/nycb-shares-eye-rebound-after-sell-off-material-weakness-disclosure-2024-03-04/</link>
